(This fight started off late but it doesn't matter)

Lash:



The fifteen foot tall Epician robot was nothing like Cybertronian design, his 
basic shape a 'T', an unknown force allowing him to hover off the ground.  
When the officials stated the fight to start, this veteran IGL fighter 
powered up, his single optic band firing out a large blast of electricity at 
Penguin 2's torso.
